videos.headline: Texas A&M blocks field goal
videos.description: Owen Hoolihan 38 yd FG BLOCKED blocked by Justin Evans

videos.headline: Texas A&M RB Ford bounces off defenders, finds end zone
videos.description: Texas A&M Keith Ford shows his elusiveness avoiding tackles by the Prairie View A&M defense and rushes 11 yards for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Knight scampers down sideline for score
videos.description: Texas A&M QB Trevor Knight escapes pressure in the pocket and runs along the sideline 32 yards for the touchdown.

videos.headline: T. Green pass intercepted,N. Ellis return  for 0 yds
videos.description: Trey Green pass intercepted Noel Ellis return for no gain to the PraVw 40

videos.headline: T. Knight pass,to S. Noil for 8 yds for a TD
videos.description: Trevor Knight pass complete to Speedy Noil for 8 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Kirk side steps defender and finds end zone
videos.description: Texas A&M WR Christian Kirk catches a pass and runs down the sideline before side stepping a Prairie View A&M defender and taking it to the house 34 yards for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Knight finds Kirk for 64-yard TD before halftime
videos.description: With less than a minute to go in the first half, Texas A&M QB Trevor Knight fires a pass to a wide open Christian Kirk for a 64-yard touchdown pass, widening the Aggies lead over Prairie View A&M.

videos.headline: Texas A&M extends the lead
videos.description: Keith Ford run for 4 yds for a TD (Daniel LaCamera KICK)

videos.headline: Aggies return punt 73 yards for score
videos.description: Texas A&M continues to pile on their big lead against Prairie View A&M after Nick Harvey returns a punt 73 yards for a touchdown.
